tel/image/upload/x_0,y_0,w_4000,h_2250,r_0,c_crop,q_80,fl_progressive/w_303,f_auto,c_fit/maurya-hotel-bangalore/DJI_0015_hvymki" style="aspect-ratio: 4000/2250; " width="455"/></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 center-box"><img alt="Maurya Hotel, Bangalore Bangalore DSC 3529" class="img-responsive image-content" height="256" src="https://assets.simplotel.com/simplotel/image/upload/w_5000,h_3338/x_0,y_263,w_5000,h_2812,r_0,c_crop,q_80,fl_progressive/w_303,f_auto,c_fit/maurya-hotel-bangalore/DSC_3529_bhzshp" style="aspect-ratio: 5000/2812; " width="455"/></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 right-box"><img alt="Maurya Hotel, Bangalore Bangalore DJI 0003" class="img-responsive image-content" height="256" src="https://assets.simplotel.com/simplotel/image/upload/x_0,y_0,w_4000,h_2250,r_0,c_crop,q_80,fl_progressive/w_303,f_auto,c_fit/maurya-hotel-bangalore/DJI_0003_bnek7v" style="aspect-ratio: 4000/2250; " width="455"/></div></div><div class="row clearfix widget-wrapper wt1tb" style="background-color: ;"><div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 one-col text-content"><p><span>The brilliant combination of a convenient location, amazing services and reasonable pricing makes the hotel one of the top destinations to stay at for both business and leisure travellers. Maurya Hotel</span>, a 3-star hotel in Bangalore, offers 3 varieties of tastefully decorated and furnished rooms to fit your requirements;<span> <a class="internal-link" data-page-id="66254" href="./rooms/deluxe-room.html" target="_self">Deluxe Room</a>, <a class="internal-link" data-page-id="66255" href="./rooms/executive-room.html" target="_self">Executive Room</a> and the <a class="internal-link" data-page-id="66256" href="./rooms/maurya-suite.html" target="_self">Maurya Suite</a>. </span><br/> <br/> <span>Each room is elegantly designed and decked with comfortable king-size beds. With all modern amenities at your disposal, your stay with us is guaranteed to be hassle-free.</span></p></div></di