ng regulars.<br/> The recently opened Rhum Bar features a wide variety of IMFL, Scotch, Rum, Beer, Cocktails and Mocktails. Good deals available during Happy Hours.</span><br/> <br/> Maurya Hotel, Bangalore, also brings to you <a class="internal-link" data-page-id="66274" href="./banquets-meetings.html" target="_self">3 stylish and well-equipped banquet and meeting halls</a>. For any event, be it small or grand, we provide all the services and venues to make sure that it is a roaring success.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="normal col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 clearfix custom-right-widget-wrapper"><div class="clearfix widget-wrapper hotel_amenities_wrap" style="background-color: ;"><p class="text-center side-nav-header no-pad-bot"><span>Hotel Amenities</span></p><ul><li><span class="hotel_amenitie_icon"><i class="far fa-briefcase"></i></span> <span class="hotel_amenitie_name">Business Center</span></li><li><span class="hotel_amenitie_icon"><i class="far fa-utensils"></i></span> <span class="hotel_amenitie_name">Restaurant</span></li><li><span class="hotel_amenitie_icon"><i class="far fa-asterisk"></i></span> <span class="hotel_amenitie_name">Complimentary Breakfast &amp; WiFi</span></li><li><span class="hotel_amenitie_icon"><i class="far fa-asterisk"></i></span> <span class="hotel_amenitie_name">Laundry service</span></li><li><span class="hotel_amenitie_icon"><i class="far fa-coffee"></i></span> <span class="hotel_amenitie_name">Tea and Coffee maker</span></li></ul></div><div class="row clearfix widget-wrapper wtlocmap" style="background-color: ;"><p class="text-center side-nav-header no-pad-bot"><span>Location</span></p><a href="./location.html"><img alt="location map" class="img-responsive" height="350" src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?key=AIzaSyBDxiAqwL5hmQypVpwmo_7ctFueIBmKRi8&amp;center=12.9808895,77.57676420000007&amp;zoom=14&amp;size=400x350&amp;maptype=roadmap&amp;markers=color:red%7C12.9808895,77.57676420000007" width="400"/></a